elilo-installer (1.4) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * Colin Watson
    - Fix name of title template so that it actually gets used.
    - Remove bogus isinstallable script; it only works if debootstrap
      installs elilo, which we're trying to avoid, and it's unnecessary
      because the postinst now apt-installs elilo and checks for failure.
    - The postinst is 'set -e'; fix logic for looking at elilo's exit code
      to cope with that.
    - Use debian-installer/elilo-installer/title for the progress bar title.
      This template doesn't quite have the ideal text, but this is the best
      we can do without breaking the string freeze.
  * Matt Kraai
    - Fix the spelling of "file system".

 -- Colin Watson <cjwatson@debian.org>  Thu, 27 Jan 2005 20:32:11 +0000

